raw_answer: ∵AD是△ABC的角平分线∠BAC=76°,∴∠DAC=∠DAB=38°,∵AE是△ABD的角平分线∴∠BAE=19°,∴∠EAD=∠BAD-∠BAE=19°.故选A.
